  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Dividing the number in each table cell by the total number of attempts provides the percentages associated with the cell number.",
    "Based on these values, we can calculate further indicators, such as accuracy, precision, recall, specificity, and F1 score.",
    "The accuracy, i.e., the proportion of correctly identified stimuli out of all stimuli in the experiment, was equal to 76.19%, 95% CI [73.16, 79.03 ].",
    "Precision, the number of correct identifications of AI out of all stimuli identified as AI, was 77.92%, 95% CI [73.49, 81.92].",
    "The recall value represents the percentage of correct identifications of the AI-generated stimuli."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "The accuracy, i.e., the proportion of correctly identified stimuli out of all stimuli in the experiment, was equal to 76.19%, 95% CI [73.16, 79.03 ].",
    "Precision, the number of correct identifications of AI out of all stimuli identified as AI, was 77.92%, 95% CI [73.49, 81.92]."
  ]
